skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: screen test
des:
Do you talk in movie quotes? Test your movie quote skills with the Screen Test | Movie Quote Quiz. 

Alexa will play several famous movie clips. You name the title of the movie. Each correct answer includes facts about the movie. If the movie is on the tip of your tongue you can repeat the quote, get a clue, or ask more time.

Movie quotes from the 1930s to today. Now with over 200 movie clips! New quotes added weekly. Famous quotes include:
"I feel the need for speed"
"To infinity and beyond!"
"Buddy the Elf, what's your favorite color?"



If you have issues, questions, or comments please email us at alexa@cinemaplayground.com. We want to hear directly from you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
